00:02:32.240 --> 00:02:35.440
I mistakenly thought Shangguan Feiye killed my brother.

00:02:36.120 --> 00:02:38.050
But later I remembered something.

00:02:39.240 --> 00:02:40.520
It was you who told me

00:02:41.000 --> 00:02:43.880
that evil spirits appeared in Shangguan Feiye's village.

00:02:43.880 --> 00:02:45.880
You sent me to catch those monsters.

00:02:45.960 --> 00:02:47.640
You wanted her to misunderstand

00:02:47.640 --> 00:02:49.240
that I was Dongfang Zhaobai.

00:02:49.440 --> 00:02:51.040
That I killed her loved ones.

00:02:51.720 --> 00:02:54.120
Then use her to eliminate my brother.

00:02:55.520 --> 00:02:56.240
It seems

00:02:56.600 --> 00:02:58.560
you're not as stupid as I thought.

00:02:59.360 --> 00:03:01.800
But aren't you afraid your brother

00:03:02.640 --> 00:03:05.400
might actually die from the Wujian Vine

00:03:05.400 --> 00:03:06.800
filled with karmic fire?

00:03:12.240 --> 00:03:14.680
