00:03:16.160 --> 00:03:17.020
My brother and I

00:03:17.400 --> 00:03:19.520
are incarnations of the Huangquan Jade.

00:03:19.520 --> 00:03:20.380
The Wujian Vine

00:03:20.560 --> 00:03:22.220
connects the two jade pieces.

00:03:22.480 --> 00:03:25.079
