00:03:26.320 --> 00:03:27.200
Karmic fire!

00:03:28.079 --> 00:03:30.010
So what if it's a different person?

00:03:30.360 --> 00:03:31.120
Besides,

00:03:31.760 --> 00:03:33.960
now you bear the power of karmic fire.

00:03:34.400 --> 00:03:36.480
You'll soon be reduced to ashes.

00:03:37.079 --> 00:03:38.560
What can you possibly do?

00:03:40.600 --> 00:03:42.930
It was all just an illusion to deceive you.

00:03:43.720 --> 00:03:44.960
When you thought my brother

00:03:44.960 --> 00:03:47.560
was completely controlled by the Wujian Vine,

00:03:47.680 --> 00:03:49.520
I transferred it to myself.

00:03:51.079 --> 00:03:51.680
