00:03:52.800 --> 00:03:53.930
I was also gambling.

00:03:54.960 --> 00:03:56.620
Betting that Shangguan Feiye

00:03:56.920 --> 00:03:57.980
would risk her life

00:03:58.440 --> 00:04:00.300
to return to a thousand years ago.

00:04:03.920 --> 00:04:05.120
So what?

00:04:05.960 --> 00:04:08.160
You're only half of the Huangquan Jade.

00:04:08.600 --> 00:04:10.660
Now you bear the power of karmic fire.

00:04:10.800 --> 00:04:12.680
You'll soon be reduced to ashes.

00:04:13.960 --> 00:04:15.880
As for those two,

00:04:16.519 --> 00:04:18.519
